{"type": "article", "id": 24226, "title": "喜欢软软的“手套鞋”吗？这里有 4 双", "description": "Céline 捧红了这双鞋。", "date": "2016-03-22T15:47:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 25213, "name": "手套鞋"}, {"id": 25214, "name": "奶奶鞋"}, {"id": 25222, "name": ".Martiniano"}, {"id": 25223, "name": "Maryam Nassir Zadeh"}, {"id": 25224, "name": "Jasper & Jeera"}], "category": 19, "author": 399912, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060716425594batE8B0fYhRdOs.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">说来也奇怪，这世上用起来太舒服的东西长得都不会太好看。特别是对于鞋子来说，这简直算是一条金规玉律。<br></p>\n<p>最近很走红的手套鞋，也有人称作老奶奶鞋，大概就是这么个路数。手套鞋看起来就像一双手套，软软包住双脚，鞋跟都以平跟和中跟为主，看起来很复古。不过，要不是皮革的面料，和北京老布鞋还真有那么点神似。除了五颜六色称得算有几分姿色，其他细节可算得上是皮鞋界的极简派别，和现在流行的性冷淡风搭配起来正好合适。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.elle.com/fashion/shopping/g28009/best-glove-shoes-for-spring/?slide=5\">Elle 做一个品牌的清单，</a>手套鞋的鼻祖 Martiniano ，还有让它走红的 Céline，当然也有高街品牌 Zara , Topshop 等，它们都在一定程度上对手套鞋做了一些改良。我们挑了其中 4 个。</p>\n<h2>1.Martiniano</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164246MidobcnD3usHzt2e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33012048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164246pjioaPw90I75EOUG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95454545\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164247kcDyB9jngd276QUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94639866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164247vg7nSlJw8NQkMBLh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95286195\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164248uDrpJQtTnNGM3Few.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">2011 年，阿根廷的独立设计师 Martiniano Lopez Crozet 做了这种手套鞋，据说最初是为男士设计。平跟的手套鞋价格稍便宜，在 395 美元左右，高跟版本贵一些，价格在 515 美元左右。</p>\n<h2>2.Céline</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071642485Pohmt0dbSAC4Lnq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164249x72QvumfWe6MsLwS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164249SC6XmT2s7fIikuxw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.45431472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164250gfDzo9LQ285NV4xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.49846154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Martiniano 是手套鞋的发明者，Céline  算是推出了改良版，而且还把这种鞋带火了。Céline  的版本在鞋跟上做了文章，鞋跟更粗更宽，像梯形。另外，Céline  不仅推出了春款，冬款的手套鞋的皮革看起来更坚硬，但基本保持了手套鞋的形状。</p>\n<h2>3.Maryam Nassir Zadeh</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164250KvsRCiIMBx2Qw4oU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071642511j3wyqOiA0NmJEYt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73432836\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060716425247HSlaPfy5cVNFt0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Maryam Nassir Zadeh 也推出了手套鞋，不过颜色更鲜艳靓丽，有粉蓝、粉红，明黄等，采用了麂皮材质的面料。</p>\n<h2>4.Jasper &amp; Jeera</h2>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164253ayzYZdBuwpDS20FA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49812734\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164253rtO7J2PeuRY6I3Ll.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607164254jeRWBP86tJYq7p2H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060716425469cN75ohDwunjkTx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50117647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>Jasper &amp; Jeera 做的手套鞋的版本并不太多，平日的设计素来走的是民族风。所以，这个品牌做的手套鞋比较朴素的，浅色的木制鞋跟算是特色。</p>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/martinianoshoes/\">Martiniano @ instagram</a>、<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/512706738806663912/\">pinterest</a>、<a href=\"http://www.whowhatwear.com/celine-shoe-trend\">whowhatwear</a>、<a href=\"http://www.bhv.fr/author/s-hoareau/\">bhv</a>、<a href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/search/high%20glove%20white%20shoe\">tumblr</a>、<a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/229894755953979602/\">pinterest</a>、<a href=\"http://www.savoirflair.com/accessories/120625/maryam-nassir-zadeh-accessories\">savoirflair</a>、<a href=\"http://www.anthropologie.com/us/product/shoes-heels/38675096.jsp\">anthropologie</a>。<br></p>\n\n\n"}